<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Fresh Coupon Drop</title>
    <style>
        /* --- RESET & BODY --- */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        /* --- MAIN CONTAINER --- */
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 550px;
            width: 100%;
            background: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin: 20px;
        }

        /* --- HEADER (Electric Blue to Purple Gradient) --- */
        /* Thoda change kiya for "Fresh" look */
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4F46E5 0%, #7C3AED 100%);
            padding: 45px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        /* --- COOL TEXT AREA --- */
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hype-headline {
            color: #111;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .hype-body {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            max-width: 400px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        /* --- TICKET CONTAINER --- */
        .ticket-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1));
            max-width: 460px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px auto;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .ticket-wrapper:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        /* Left Side (Bright Yellow) */
        .ticket-left {
            background-color: #FFC107;
            width: 65%;
            border-top-left-radius: 16px;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 16px;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;

            /* Cutout */
            mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 0 50%, transparent 12px, black 13px);
            -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 0 50%, transparent 12px, black 13px);
        }

        .vertical-text {
            writing-mode: vertical-rl;
            transform: rotate(180deg);
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 3px;
            color: #111;
            border-left: 2px solid #111;
            padding-left: 12px;
            margin-right: 18px;
            height: 90px;
            text-align: center;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .offer-content h2 {
            font-size: 52px;
            line-height: 0.9;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: #111;
            margin: 0;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
        }

        .offer-tag {
            background: #000;
            color: #FFC107;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            border-radius: 4px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .offer-sub {
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #111;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        /* Divider */
        .divider {
            position: absolute;
            right: 0;
            top: 15px;
            bottom: 15px;
            border-right: 2px dashed rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        /* Right Side (White) */
        .ticket-right {
            background-color: #fff;
            width: 35%;
            border-top-right-radius: 16px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 16px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;

            /* Cutout */
            mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 100% 50%, transparent 12px, black 13px);
            -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 100% 50%, transparent 12px, black 13px);
        }

        .code-box {
            border: 2px dashed #e5e7eb;
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .code {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #111;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .expiry-text {
            font-size: 10px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* --- BUTTON --- */
        .btn {
            background-color: #111;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 18px 45px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 16px;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

        /* --- FOOTER --- */
        .footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            border-top: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
            padding-top: 20px;
        }

        /* --- MOBILE-OPTIMIZED SIDE-BY-SIDE TICKET --- */
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .email-wrapper {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 16px;
            }

            .header {
                padding: 30px 15px;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 25px 15px;
            }

            /* Ticket Container Adjustments */
            .ticket-wrapper {
                display: flex !important;
                /* Force side-by-side */
                flex-direction: row !important;
                max-width: 100%;
                filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1));
            }

            .ticket-left {
                width: 60%;
                /* Mobile pe left side thoda chhota */
                padding: 15px 10px;
                mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 0 50%, transparent 8px, black 9px);
                -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 0 50%, transparent 8px, black 9px);
            }

            .vertical-text {
                font-size: 8px;
                /* Bahut chhota font */
                letter-spacing: 1px;
                margin-right: 8px;
                padding-left: 6px;
                height: 60px;
            }

            .offer-content h2 {
                font-size: 32px;
                /* Price mobile ke hisaab se adjust */
            }

            .offer-tag {
                font-size: 9px;
                padding: 2px 5px;
            }

            .offer-sub {
                font-size: 10px;
            }

            /* Right Side (Code Area) */
            .ticket-right {
                width: 40%;
                padding: 10px;
                mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 100% 50%, transparent 8px, black 9px);
                -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(circle at 100% 50%, transparent 12px, black 13px);
            }

            .code-box {
                padding: 5px 8px;
                border-radius: 6px;
            }

            .code {
                font-size: 14px;
                /* Code size adjusted to fit */
            }

            .expiry-text {
                font-size: 8px;
            }

            .btn {
                padding: 15px 30px;
                font-size: 14px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Just Landed 🚀</h1>
            <p>Hot, fresh, and ready for you.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">

            <div class="hype-headline">It doesn't get fresher than this!</div>
            <div class="hype-body">
                We just activated this exclusive code moments ago.
                Skip the queue and grab your discount while the oven is still hot.
            </div>

            <div class="ticket-wrapper">

                <div class="ticket-left">
                    <div class="vertical-text">EXCLUSIVE</div>
                    <div class="offer-content">
                        <span class="offer-tag">Live Now</span>
                        <h2>{{discountText}}</h2>
                        <div class="offer-sub">{{discountType}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="divider"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="ticket-right">
                    <div class="code-box">
                        <span class="code">{{code}}</span>
                    </div>
                    <span class="expiry-text">Valid till {{validUntil}}</span>
                </div>

            </div>

            <a href="#" class="btn">CLAIM MY FOOD &rarr;</a>

            <div class="footer">
                &copy; {{year}} FoodDelivery. Sent with ⚡ speed.
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>

</html>